1. My build system/runtime is: Bun
2. My backend framework is: Elysia (elysia@latest)
3. Database: MongoDB (via Mongoose mongoose@^8.13.0)
4. Authentication:
- JWT (@elysiajs/jwt@^1.2.0)
- bcryptjs (bcryptjs@^2.4.3)
5. API Docs: Swagger (@elysiajs/swagger@^1.2.2)
6. CORS: @elysiajs/cors@^1.2.0
7. Email: Nodemailer (nodemailer@^6.10.0)
8. HTTP Client: Axios (axios@^1.8.4)
9. Date/Time: Moment.js (moment@^2.30.1)
10. TypeScript types: bun-types, @types for bcryptjs and nodemailer